name: PRODUCERS WITH COMPUTERS - VOLUME 1 - sold out
description:
The first ever official CD/product of the infamous underground alternative hip-hop act, Producers With Computers.

A twenty-one track mixtape featuring "appearances" from the likes of Scroobius Pip, Coldplay, The Secret Handshake and many more.

1. Volume 1 Intro
2. Girlies
3. Face Down - The Jump Off
4. Stupid
5. WKTYLU

9. Cnut part 2

11. Ghost
12. Dog Eat Dog Feat. Scroobius Pip
13. Tied Up
14. Get that drop
15. Skit Answering Machine Message
16. Anchorman Dub
17. Colon Bracket
18. Arthur REMIX

If you like Producers With Computers, you NEED this.

description:
Producers With Computers second mixtape on their massive build-up to their album sees them explore new sounds and subjects.

Featuring big underground hits like SLAG and MY LOVE SONG this is a definite PWC hardcore fans buy.
